conversations.value: In this video, report "Out of Stock" if the target product is taken from the shelf a specified number of times by the custmers. Report when it was, as an incident. The time must be output from the time of the movie itself. If the count is less than the specified number at the end of the video, report "Out of Stock Not Detected". Do not count when the product is placed back. Target product : light olive-colored box. specified number : 5
